<h2 class="h3"><strong>Get help to quit smoking</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/your-health/healthy-living/addictions/quitting-smoking">View our quitting smoking page</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://quitstrong.nz/">QuitStrong - Kia kaha, you&#39;ve got this!</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.smokefree.org.nz/help-advice/stop-smoking-services">Smokefree.org</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://quit.org.nz/">Quit.org</a></li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Making a complaint</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/preventative-health-wellness/tobacco-control/smokefree-environments-legislation/complaints-under-smokefree-environments-and-regulated-products-act-1990">Smokefree complaints</a></li>
</ul>

